                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Innovation</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">
                            We embrace creativity and forward-thinking solutions to enhance guest experiences.
                        </p>
